\cf0 Preheat oven to 250 degrees F.\
Toss oats, almonds, coconut and sesame seeds in a large bowl.\
Whisk syrup, brown sugar, oil, warm water and salt in bowl to blend\
Pour syrup mixture over oat mixture and combine well.\
Transfer to baking sheet and bake until evenly brown stirring occasionally, about 1 hour and 15 minutes. \
Cool completely.  Transfer to large bowl and  mix in raisins.\
Double dry ingredients and triple wet ingredients, if desired. 
